      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Version-controlled solver with documented regression test suite covering hemolysis-relevant flow regimes; formal change-control process in place.",
      "rationale": "The CFD solver (ANSYS Fluent 2022 R2) is under institutional version control and a regression suite of 14 canonical cases is maintained. However, no formal change-control process exists for in-house hemolysis scalar transport UDFs. Achieved level 2 against required level 3."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Numerical code verification",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
