      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Order-of-accuracy verification for both Navier-Stokes solver and hemolysis power-law scalar transport equation using manufactured solutions or benchmark problems.",
      "rationale": "Order-of-accuracy testing was completed for the Navier-Stokes equations on the Taylor-Green vortex benchmark (observed order 1.94 vs. theoretical 2.0). The hemolysis power-law UDF was not subjected to manufactured-solution verification; a simple residual check was used instead. Achieved level 2 against required level 3."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Discretization error",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 4,
