      "acceptanceCriteria": "Iterative convergence to residual tolerance < 1e-6 for all equations including hemolysis scalar; round-off error analysis for double-precision arithmetic documented.",
      "rationale": "Iterative convergence was monitored but residual tolerances for the hemolysis scalar transport equation were not reported separately from the flow equations. Round-off error analysis was not performed. Factor not assessed at the required level; flagged as epistemic gap at MRL 5. Achieved level 1 against required level 3."
    },
